      <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
        <from>MR. SPEAKER</from>
        <p>MR. SPEAKER : Order, please. Before we start the daily routine, the subject for late debate has been submitted and accepted:</p>
      </speech>
      <debateSection>
        <heading>TABLING REPORTS, REGULATIONS AND OTHER PAPERS</heading>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
          <from>MR. SPEAKER</from>
          <p>MR. SPEAKER : As the Speaker, I am tabling the Nova Scotia MLA Pension Review Report, dated November 3, 2011. I am having the Pages distribute the report to any members who would like a printed copy. The entire report is available on-line so if any members don't really need one of these printed copies, you could just tell the Pages. We printed a very limited number of copies to keep the cost down.</p>
        </speech>
      </debateSection>
      <debateSection>
        <heading>GOVERNMENT NOTICES OF MOTION</heading>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
