        <speech by="#a17abcb6-45ac-4a02-a639-9e63df869d46">
          <from>HON. DAVID WILSON</from>
          <p>HON. DAVID WILSON: Mr. Speaker, on behalf of the Premier, I hereby give notice that on a future day I shall move the adoption of the following resolution:</p>
